data.description: Custom built, this home is immaculately kept 4/2 brick home is awaiting its new owner. Nice kitchen with custom oak cabinet's , gorgeous granite and tons of storage.  Beautiful private back yard perfect for all gatherings, enjoy your private patio  deck,  Some of the features include: Beautiful flooring, a sitting room/ office in the Master Bedroom,  Solar screens on the sunroom, storage shed and much more. The tool room off of the garage will help keep the garage straight.  There are many more features but you really need to come see this beautiful home. All updates per the seller. Listing company makes no representation as to accuracy of square footage; buyer to verify.
